data.description: Welcome home! This gorgeous ranch w/ full basement is custom throughout! Main level boasts gleaming hardwoods, expansive primary suite, office, dining rm (currently used as music room), and gourmet kitchen! An expansive deck leads from great rm overlooking wooded lot. Custom cabinetry throughout! Kitchen w/ spacious cabinets, countertops and huge walk-in pantry. Butler's pantry w/ custom cabinetry & wine refrigerator. Laundry rm boasts plenty of storage. The basement is perfect for entertaining or extended family! The second kitchen downstairs is spacious & conveniently located. The downstairs great rm offers a gas fireplace w/ beautiful stonework. One secondary bedroom downstairs (currently used for a craft room) boasts a built-in electric fireplace. A huge walk-in closet is also provided for storage. The other secondary bedrm downstairs provides an ensuite bathrm and huge walk-in closet. Large patio at the lower level! This home has so much storage! Location near Blakeney and I-485!
